<SYNC Start=57849><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=62458><P Class=ENCC>
죽지마!
<SYNC Start=67828><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=87116><P Class=ENCC>
어제일은 미안해.
<SYNC Start=88606><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=90219><P Class=ENCC>
신경쓰지마.
<SYNC Start=91948><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=97660><P Class=ENCC>
여기 부적이야.
<SYNC Start=101619><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=102832><P Class=ENCC>
전쟁에서 너 보호해 줄꺼야.
<SYNC Start=104595><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=106302><P Class=ENCC>
고마워.
<SYNC Start=108099><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=114143><P Class=ENCC>
버스왔네.
<SYNC Start=115770><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=119248><P Class=ENCC>
나 히로시마 군수공장에서 <BR>
일하게 될꺼야.
<SYNC Start=123480><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=125721><P Class=ENCC>
너 쉬엄쉬엄해야되.
<SYNC Start=128212><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=156852><P Class=ENCC>
어서 타세요.
<SYNC Start=159082><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=161557><P Class=ENCC>
출발.
<SYNC Start=162421><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=164794><P Class=ENCC>
힘내.
<SYNC Start=166022><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=176772><P Class=ENCC>
갑니다.
<SYNC Start=178330><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=178841><P Class=ENCC>
