<SYNC Start=258680><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=262324><P Class=ENCC>
여보!
<SYNC Start=263916><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=264994><P Class=ENCC>
